# Alert dispatcher's file-fallback drop zone (lib/alerts/channels/*).
# Populated whenever SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL / GENERIC_WEBHOOK_URL are unset, or
# when v1 email writes its .eml stub. Test runs accumulate files here;
# never check in.
outbox/

# Phase 6 application package — PRIVATE BY DEFAULT. Contains the
# job-application artifacts: evidence-pack.json (may name a hiring
# manager), personalized outreach (.eml/.txt), and the cover letter.
# Uploaded to the careers portal directly, NOT pushed to the repo.
#
# Ignore the CONTENTS glob (`application/*`), NOT the directory
# (`application/`): git cannot re-include a file inside a
# fully-ignored directory, but CAN inside a directory whose contents
# are ignored. This keeps the plan's selective-publish escape hatch
# working — e.g. `!application/architecture-essay.md` to publish only
# the non-personal architecture essay as a writing sample, while
# evidence-pack.json and the outreach files stay private.
application/*
